{
  "description": "A close-up, low-angle shot showcases three vibrant red tulips in full bloom. The tulips are positioned against a soft, slightly blurred, blue sky. The light source appears to be behind and slightly to the left of the flowers, creating dramatic shadows and highlighting the velvety texture of the petals. The inner parts of the tulips reveal a bright yellow core, providing a striking contrast to the deep red outer petals. The stems are visible, adding to the sense of natural growth. The focus is sharp on the tulips, and the composition is dominated by their round shapes and rich color.",
